[SN]TITLE[SN]
Music-loving pet pot-bellied pig celebrates his third birthday

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A Vietnamese pot-bellied pig who has moved to Derby is apparently a music-loving pet.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is unsupported on your device
19 January 2015 Last updated at 17:00 GMT
He can play a small toy piano and is even named after a musician.
Ludwig recently celebrated his third birthday with his owners Liane Scholz and Mike Maughan.
Simon Ward reports.
